<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="413">Etymology.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="413">The new species is named in honor of Dr. Ralph W. Holzenthal (University of Minnesota, USA) in recognition of his efforts to the advancement of the knowledge on Neotropical caddisflies and his contributions in supervising new entomologists.</paragraph>
